---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Follow by RSS
description: Learn what the Democratic Justice RSS feed is and how to use it.
permalink: /rss/index.html
ogType: website
kicker: Follow
---
{% set feedUrl = "/feed.xml" | absoluteUrl(site.url) %}
<section class="space-y-10" data-pagefind-body>
  <header class="border-b-2 border-[rgb(var(--rule-strong))] pb-6">
    <p class="section-kicker">{{ kicker }}</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-[clamp(2.7rem,5vw,4.4rem)] font-black tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">
      Follow by RSS
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
      RSS gives readers a direct feed of new reporting. Subscribe once and each new story appears in your reader.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <button class="button-link-muted" type="button" data-copy-link data-copy-value="{{ feedUrl }}" data-copy-label-default="Copy feed URL" data-copy-label-success="Feed URL copied">
        Copy feed URL
      </button>
      <a class="button-link" href="{{ feedUrl }}">Open feed URL</a>
      <a class="button-link-muted" href="/archives/">Browse the archive</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="grid gap-8 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.15fr)_18rem]">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section class="listing-card p-6 md:p-7">
        <p class="section-kicker">How it works</p>
        <div class="mt-5 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="space-y-3">
            <p class="font-ui text-[0.7rem] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[rgb(var(--ink-muted))]">Step 1</p>
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">Copy the feed URL</h2>
            <p class="font-serif text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
              Copy the Democratic Justice feed address.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="space-y-3">
            <p class="font-ui text-[0.7rem] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[rgb(var(--ink-muted))]">Step 2</p>
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">Paste it into any RSS reader</h2>
            <p class="font-serif text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
              Use the add-feed or subscribe-by-URL option in your reader.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="space-y-3">
            <p class="font-ui text-[0.7rem] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[rgb(var(--ink-muted))]">Step 3</p>
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">Read new stories automatically</h2>
            <p class="font-serif text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
              New stories appear in your reader when they are published.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="listing-card p-6 md:p-7">
        <p class="section-kicker">Feed URL</p>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl font-serif text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
          This is the address you paste into a feed reader:
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 border border-[rgba(var(--rule),0.92)] bg-[rgba(var(--paper-muted),0.7)] px-4 py-4">
          <code class="block overflow-x-auto font-ui text-sm font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--ink))]">{{ feedUrl }}</code>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="listing-card p-6 md:p-7">
        <p class="section-kicker">Why we offer it</p>
        <div class="mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-4 font-serif text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
          <p>
            RSS gives readers a direct feed of new reporting.
          </p>
          <p>
            It also gives the publication a stable feed readers can archive, cite, and return to.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="space-y-4 xl:pt-1">
      <div class="tool-card p-5 xl:sticky xl:top-6">
        <p class="section-kicker">What you get</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--ink-soft))]">
          <li>Full-story entries from the publication feed.</li>
          <li>A permanent URL for each story.</li>
          <li>A direct feed of new reporting.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
          <button class="button-link-muted w-full justify-center" type="button" data-copy-link data-copy-value="{{ feedUrl }}" data-copy-label-default="Copy feed URL" data-copy-label-success="Feed URL copied">
            Copy feed URL
          </button>
          <a class="button-link w-full justify-center" href="{{ feedUrl }}">Open feed URL</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
